nodes.text: Timeline 17: The Jedi Order is Established

Timeline 17: The Jedi Order is Established would have been the seventeenth in the series of in-universe videos, providing backstory for the Star Wars: The Old Republic video game. The video would have been presented in the form of a record entry made in the Jedi Archives by Jedi Master Gnost-Dural.
The remaining Timeline videos were discontinued in early 2011, as the content was growing less relevant to the game.
Peace-minded scholars and monks who survived the explosive Force War on Tython relocated and established the Jedi Order.
